criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Participants not physically active;

          2. Partially/uncontrolled asthma;

          3. Diagnosis of asthma based on the recommendations of the Global Initiative for Asthma
             (GINA 2020);

          4. Be under outpatient follow-up at the Pulmonology or Immunology service of the
             University of Sao Paulo General Hospital;

          5. Be under outpatient medical treatment for at least six months, with a stable clinical
             condition for at least , 30 days;

          6. Being using optimized drug therapy for asthma.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Participation in another research protocol;

          2. Difficulty in understanding any of the questionnaires used;

          3. Practitioners of regular physical activity;

          4. Pregnancy and psychiatric problems that make it difficult to understand the
             questionnaires and the study protocol.
